### VentaPagos API Examples

### 1. Create a Pedido with VentaPagos
POST https://localhost:7000/Pedidos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "clienteId": 1,
  "pedidoProductos": [
    {
      "productoId": 1,
      "cantidad": 2
    }
  ],
  "ventaPagos": [
    {
      "metodo": 0,
      "monto": 100.50
    },
    {
      "metodo": 1,
      "monto": 50.00
    }
  ],
  "metodoPago": 0
}

### 2. Get all VentaPagos
GET https://localhost:7000/VentaPagos
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 3. Get VentaPagos by ID
GET https://localhost:7000/VentaPagos/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 4. Get VentaPagos by VentaId (Pedido ID)
GET https://localhost:7000/VentaPagos/venta/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 5. Create a new VentaPagos
POST https://localhost:7000/VentaPagos
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "ventaId": 1,
  "metodo": 2,
  "monto": 75.25
}

### 6. Update VentaPagos
PUT https://localhost:7000/VentaPagos/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "id": 1,
  "ventaId": 1,
  "metodo": 0,
  "monto": 100.00
}

### 7. Delete VentaPagos
DELETE https://localhost:7000/VentaPagos/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 8. Get Pedido with VentaPagos included
GET https://localhost:7000/Pedidos/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### MetodoPagoEnum values:
### 0 = Efectivo
### 1 = Transferencia  
### 2 = Tarjeta
### 3 = CuentaCorriente
